ParallelChunk.en:
The debate on the future of Europe involved all the main players; it took place in the full light of day; 
          and
         it produced a coherent text on which the Intergovernmental Conference has been able to work effectively.

The Commission is inclined to keep these transitional periods that have been adopted by many countries as short as possible; 
          indeed
        , for the Commission, it would have been much better if they had not been adopted.

ParallelChunk.fr:
La Commission est encline à maintenir ces périodes de transition adoptées par de nombreux pays le moins de temps possible; 
          en effet
        , la Commission est d’avis qu’il aurait mieux valu ne pas les adopter.
